data.description: Adorable 1.5 story home in the heart of Higginsville.  It features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, main floor master, open concept, and has been recently updated.  Refrigerator, dishwasher, stove, washer, and dryer will all remain with the home.  It is on a huge corner lot with a large detached 2- car garage/ workshop.  There is a cute covered front porch, a large deck off the second level, close to the schools, and so much more.  Call today for a private showing and make this home yours!
